entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Rian Ry has offered your name to the Civil Protection Guild commander here on Kashyyyk. You'll find him near the starport in Kachirho.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Report to Civilian Protection Guild commander on Kashyyyk
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Eyma can be found near the starport here in Kachirho. Speak to him and provide the information he needs.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Speak with Eyma the Civilian Protection Guild commander
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Provide Eyma a report of your encounters with the Ghrag mercenary clan
